Begini saja, aku akan mengajarimu
tiga elemen dalam berakting.

155
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:43,580
Dengarkan, perhatikan,
dan rasakan baik-baik.

156
00:08:44,290 --> 00:08:44,460
Oke?

157
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:45,730
Ayo, semua departemen bersiap.

158
00:08:45,730 --> 00:08:46,700
Baik, aku sudah datang.

159
00:08:48,970 --> 00:08:49,380
Ingatlah.

160
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:50,850
Nyalakan kamera.

161
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:54,410
Tiga, dua, satu, mulai!

162
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:58,170
[Rekam]

163
00:08:58,170 --> 00:08:59,820
Menurutku, para pimpinan
yang ada saat ini

164
